  <para>
    The purpose of this document is to describe how the different
    pieces of Ulteo OVD are supported on Debian Lenny system.
  </para>

  <section id="prerequisites">
    <title>Prerequisites: Debian Lenny</title>

    <para>
      Debian Lenny is the old stable version of Debian since the
      release of Squeeze in february 2011. It can be downloaded <ulink
      url="http://www.debian.org/">here</ulink>.
    </para>

    <important>
      <para>
        The new version is Debian 6.0 Squeeze. If you don't really
        need to use Debian 5.0 Lenny version, it's higly recommanded
        to use the latest stable version: Debian 6.0 Squeeze and read
        the Debian 6.0 Squeeze documentation.
    </para>
    </important>

    <xi:include href="&parent;" xpointer="prerequisites_root" />

